{"orig":"/Users/kalaverin/src/lang/nim/lib/std/private/since.nim","nimble":"stdlib","moduleDescription":"<p><tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">since</span></span></tt> is used to emulate older versions of nim stdlib, see <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">tuse_version</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">nim</span></span></tt>.</p>\n<p>If a symbol <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">foo</span></span></tt> is added in version <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"DecNumber\">1</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"DecNumber\">3</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"DecNumber\">5</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span></span></tt>, use <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">since</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"FloatNumber\">1.3</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"DecNumber\">5</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">}</span></span></tt>, not <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">since</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"FloatNumber\">1.4</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">}</span></span></tt>, so that it works in devel in between releases.</p>\n<p>The emulation cannot be 100% faithful and to avoid adding too much complexity, <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">since</span></span></tt> is not needed in those cases:</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\"><li>if a new module is added</li>\n<li>if an overload is added</li>\n<li>if an extra parameter to an existing routine is added</li>\n</ul>\n","entries":[{"name":"since","type":"skTemplate","line":15,"col":0,"code":"template since(version: (int, int); body: untyped) {.dirty.}","signature":{"arguments":[{"name":"version","type":"(int, int)"},{"name":"body","type":"untyped"}],"pragmas":["dirty"]},"description":"<p>Evaluates <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">body</span></span></tt> if the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">(NimMajor, NimMinor)</span></tt> is greater than or equal to <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">version</span></span></tt>. Usage:</p>\n<p><pre class=\"listing\"><span class=\"Keyword\">proc</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">fun</span><span class=\"Operator\">*</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"Punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">since</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"DecNumber\">1</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"DecNumber\">3</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"Identifier\">since</span> <span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"DecNumber\">1</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"DecNumber\">3</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">fun</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span></pre></p>\n"},{"name":"since","type":"skTemplate","line":25,"col":0,"code":"template since(version: (int, int, int); body: untyped) {.dirty.}","signature":{"arguments":[{"name":"version","type":"(int, int, int)"},{"name":"body","type":"untyped"}],"pragmas":["dirty"]},"description":"<p>Evaluates <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">body</span></span></tt> if <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">(NimMajor, NimMinor, NimPatch)</span></tt> is greater than or equal to <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">version</span></span></tt>. Usage:</p>\n<p><pre class=\"listing\"><span class=\"Keyword\">proc</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">fun</span><span class=\"Operator\">*</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"Punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">since</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"DecNumber\">1</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"DecNumber\">3</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"DecNumber\">1</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"Identifier\">since</span> <span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"DecNumber\">1</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"DecNumber\">3</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"DecNumber\">1</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">fun</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span></pre></p>\n"}]}